@ChairmansLedger @FransBakker9812 @SemiAnalysis_ Photonics took a hit when SA wrote a piece on them. Nvidia took a smaller hit it that’s since it’s lower beta. 

Frans confirms there will be no dedicated piece on IREN though. 

This a short term but I monitor IREN very closely.

